<br />Latest nsf version it sounds fine.
<br />
<br />Other minor quips: the original and ost has a less severe volume envelope on the super-short notes on the boss battle theme (and in a few other places I can't think of atm), but it may be impossible to replicate that on the nes. as you said.
<br />
<br />Btw if there's one song you should redo as mml in famitracker, it should be that completely insane 'maze of death' one, just to prove that it can be done in MML.
